				<td><img src="/skins/default/images/user_IsOffline.gif" alt="Sirioh is not online. Last active: 11/28/2004 8:26:14 PM" border="0" />&nbsp;<a class="SmallBoldText" href="/User/UserProfile.aspx?UserName=Sirioh">Sirioh</a><br></td>
