				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Adding a third to my duo... but what?<a name="57448"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Aug 19 04 3:05 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I would say:
<br />
-First choice beastlord. Able to hold agro, slow better than a bard, fairly good DPS. However, not great for tanking heavy DPS mobs, leading to my next choice...
<br />
-Shadowknight. Great for tanking, better mitigation and taps will probably make up for lack of bst slow, but bard has to play an extra song = bad for multiboxing. Able to nuke for extra damage in a pinch. Pet is crap, so you can't offtank with it in any situation you would want it to. Bst pet also has stun. </span></td>
