				<td colspan="2"><span>bard/cleric/warrior here.
<br />
At lvl 65 I am glad that I choose a warrior. 
<br />
The reason: The mobs wich can be soloed are camped most of the time. With my combo I can aim for bigger mobs. Kly heartpiecer or several other god mobs come in mind. Ill guess it would be hard to tank with another class than a warrior.
<br />
The bard slows first, the warrior assist and taunt/berate, the bard hasten and regen mana/health etc., the cleric is the ch-mono chain. Works fine. 
<br />
For better mobility I added a druid several weeks before. Now I have a backup healer which can also snare and nuke a bit.
<br />
Dont know if this game was meant to be played like that but its really funny.
