Funny, I would think that with you playing a ranger you would know their potential.  Go out with your ranger if you have AM3 and EQ and GotF and a Featherwood Bow and chanter haste with all the shammy buffs you can buy in PoK.  Then run up to PoV or BoT and find a friend that is in a group and tell them &quot;I am going to try to KS you on the next pull&quot;  If they say good luck, hit TS and GotF and start shooting. Do not cast just shoot.  You may need to use your Stonewood Bow but the Featherwood should do it just fine.  THe mob will be dead befor eyour TS wears off I guarentee it. As long as they do not root the mob you will KS them and I guarentee it. If you have those AAs and gear that puts you to 1500 ATK or more self buffed with max Dex you will do it.  Unless of course there is a ranger in their group doing the same thing.....</span></td>
